{"tid":2046144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警方向支聯會發反對通知書　禁六四維園燭光會","createTime":"2020-06-01T08:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T08:23:03.000Z","uid":319512,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"36cae0efa6ea1df712c314e0bc09d7765fa4b958","tid":2046144,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:22:14.000Z","msg":"警方向支聯會發出反對通知書，禁止支聯會6月4日晚上在維園舉行六四燭光晚會。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會秘書蔡耀昌表示，會考慮提出上訴，現階段會繼續準備「Plan B」方案，當晚會擺放街站，支聯會成員亦會進入維園，燃點紀念燭光，並舉行網上集會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529548-20200601.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529548-20200601.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=11a76ef1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529548-20200601.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6083027f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529548-20200601.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6a48f1acd695da58c840b88259e8a533ceb02d99","tid":2046144,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36cae0efa6ea1df712c314e0bc09d7765fa4b958","tid":2046144,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:22:14.000Z","msg":"警方向支聯會發出反對通知書，禁止支聯會6月4日晚上在維園舉行六四燭光晚會。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會秘書蔡耀昌表示，會考慮提出上訴，現階段會繼續準備「Plan B」方案，當晚會擺放街站，支聯會成員亦會進入維園，燃點紀念燭光，並舉行網上集會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529548-20200601.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529548-20200601.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=11a76ef1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529548-20200601.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6083027f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk